description:
This is a 27 minute workout called '25 MIN FULL BODY PILATES WORKOUT FOR BEGINNERS (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Hope you enjoy this 25 Minute Full Body Pilates Workout for Beginners. Whether you are new to Pilates or just want to slow things down, this workout is for you. No equipment needed, just you and your mat. :)
